batchphoto
==========

An application for batch editing photos.


Features
--------

- Auto crop based on object detection (face, object on uniform background)


Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    $ pip install twine


Usage
-----

1. Auto crop and image(s) with a face:

  .. code-block:: bash

      $ batchphoto crop face *.jpg output


